    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel so heavy. like, every day is just a struggle to pretend i'm okay when i know i'm just dragging them down with me. it feels like the most loving thing would be to just step out of the way so they can actually have a chance at a real life. does that make sense?",
